		font-size: 24px;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #1d1d1f;
	}

	.mini-chip {
		width: 34px;
		height: 28px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background-color: #ffffff;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-width: 1px;
		border-style: solid;
		border-color: #e0e0e0;
	}

	.mini-text {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: #1d1d1f;
	}

	.search-box {
		height: 44px;
		flex-direction: row;
